## ISeqable.seq() method

Returns an [ISeq](./api.iseq.md) of the type's data or `undefined` if there're no values available. See [ISeq.next()](./api.iseq.next.md)

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
seq(): ISeq<T> | undefined;
```
<b>Returns:</b>

`ISeq<T> | undefined`
